          <div class="showcase-point-desc">每步填写提示内容，一键生成语音文件。训练时软件自动播报，眼睛和手只专注游戏操作。</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="showcase-point">
        <div class="showcase-point-icon">🎯</div>
        <div>
